source: crates/daemon/tests/cli_help.rs
expression: stdout
---
Manage rules

Usage: mxr rules [OPTIONS] [COMMAND]

Commands:
  list      
  show      
  add       
  edit      
  validate  
  enable    
  disable   
  delete    
  dry-run   
  history   
  help      Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
      --format <FORMAT>  [possible values: table, json, csv, ids]
  -h, --help             Print help
